description.en: The Transfer Token (TTT) is an ERC-20 based cryptocurrency developed by Atom Solutions. It is intended to be utilized as a gateway for currency exchange and overseas remittance. One of the main features of TTT is that, 50% of the fees incurred by trading and exchanging using Eternal Wallet are returned to the users, accordingly to the amount of TTT they hold within Eternal Wallet. Another feature is that Eternal Wallet, through using TTT, can provide users with the world’s most affordable currency exchange and overseas remittance, making it a revolutionary innovation in the current global state of currency exchanges.

status_updates.description:
The Transfer Token (TTT) will be listed on the exchange XT.com on May 24th!
Atom Solutions Co., Ltd. is proud to announce that its issued token TTT will be opened for trading at 14:00 on May 24th.
XT.com is a multilingual platform catering to users around the world, and we put great emphasis on this as we are also planning expansion on a global scale with our currency exchange and overseas remittance services.
This is the second new exchange listing in recent weeks.
status_updates.user_title: Manager of Partnerships & Overseas Business Department

status_updates.description:
Atom Solutions Co., Ltd. has released the Chinese edition of its website, in order to cater to the growing number of users coming from the world's most populated country.
With this addition, we aim for a broader appeal across the globe's citizens, and to increase the recognition of The Transfer Token and Eternal Wallet alike, allowing for the synergy of the two projects to greatly gain traction in not only the cryptocurrency ecosphere, but the entire global financial market.
status_updates.user_title: Manager of Partnerships & Overseas Business Department

status_updates.description:
Atom Solutions' issued token, The Transfer Token (TTT)  is set to list on LATOKEN on May 24th!
With this listing, we expect higher recognition of TTT and in turn increased liquidity of the token.
LATOKEN is a highly advanced and revolutionary exchange in regards to listing new projects, and we are sure that with the spotlight on us as a new listing, we can expect greater things for TTT.
status_updates.user_title: Manager of Partnerships & Overseas Business Department

status_updates.description:
Atom Solutions has released a demo of its new deposit-and-withdrawal App, "E-Counter".
With this App, a user will be able to deposit and withdrawal their funds within Eternal Wallet at a location most convenient to them both location and pricewise. 
Oppositely, the service enables anyone with an electronic device to set up shop for an E-Counter window, meaning that anyone can enter the business to service deposits and withdrawals through the App and earn money.
status_updates.user_title: Manager of Partnerships & Overseas Business Department
